title: #92Noon! JG/Bercich/Birk/Siny/PJ
description: Montage to kick off the show after a Border Battle win, JG on the Gophers, Bercich for a couple segments, Matt Birk and Dave Sinykin on Vikes/Packers, and Gophers coach PJ Fleck to wrap a busy Monday show!
